                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-9">9. Is this a live training, or will I watch pre-recorded videos? </a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-9" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
