                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-10">10. What platform do you use for video conferencing? </a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-10" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>We currently use the Zoom platform for video conferencing and will soon be adding more integrations with Webex and Microsoft Teams. However, all the sessions and the recordings will be available right from within our learning platform. Learners will not need to wait for any notifications or links or install any additional software. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-11">11. I have some more doubts. How can I get them cleared? </a> </div>
